model
Class Item

java.lang.Object
  model.Item

public class Item
extends java.lang.Object

A physical instance of a particular Product. An Item correpsronds to a physical container with a barcode on it. For example, a case of soda might contain 24 cans of Diet Coke. In this case, the Product is, "Diet Coke, 12 fl oz," while each phsyical can is a distinct Item.
